for the rest of our life.

1069
01:12:43.564 --> 01:12:45.833
Your double's name
is Sarah's Double,

1070
01:12:45.867 --> 01:12:47.902
so I can only assume
your name is Sarah.

1071
01:12:48.603 --> 01:12:50.571
I'm Daryl, the group leader.

1072
01:12:50.605 --> 01:12:52.940
