accepted all the blame.

1106
01:15:40.975 --> 01:15:43.010
The way you effectively argued
that the real enemy

1107
01:15:43.044 --> 01:15:44.912
isn't each other.

1108
01:15:44.945 --> 01:15:46.890
It's a system that arbitrarily
decides only one of us can live

1109
