similar in your letter.

1112
01:15:53.954 --> 01:15:55.756
Maybe you'll read it
for me someday.

1113
01:15:56.290 --> 01:15:57.691
Yeah.

1114
01:15:58.059 --> 01:15:59.293
And you're right,

1115
01:15:59.326 --> 01:16:01.896
