1180
01:22:01.188 --> 01:22:02.489
I agree.

1181
01:23:47.494 --> 01:23:48.663
Sorry I'm late.

1182
01:23:48.696 --> 01:23:50.430
Which one are you?

1183
01:23:50.464 --> 01:23:52.767
