1211
01:26:04.398 --> 01:26:07.735
And, finally,
do you solemnly swear

1212
01:26:07.769 --> 01:26:10.437
that you are
who you say you are?

1213
01:26:12.607 --> 01:26:13.841
I'm Sarah.

